{
  "stem": "24212.1",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.8,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So we created a gadget.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we have that gadget in the United States, sold for good money.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "It's a piece of metal.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And the child sits on it and slides down the hill.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Now what it that called?",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I gave it-- I don't know whether your TV camera can stand it-- but-- but I translated it in my book as ass sled.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "I don't want to spell that, but leave it to your imagination.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "So that's how we got them downhill.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 40,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And then uphill, they had to pull this gimmick or gadget.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But then, of course, trouble started with the Jews in Slovakia.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And so the Jews started fleeing.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 41,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And evidently, somebody from among the Jews contacted the resistance leadership.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And so then they said well, no-- no Frenchmen this time, but there is a Jewish family.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Would you take them?",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we said, well, why not?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 42,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It makes no difference to us.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And I think we must have looked at ourselves like, wow, look what we are doing.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We are spiting Hitler.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We just based this on the resistance.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And so from then on, we started taking Jews here and there.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Another Frenchman got away from a camp in Poland.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But then we took Jews.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 43,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And that, again, is in my book description, what troubles we had with some of the people, passengers that we took.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 44,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Well I was a teenager.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, definitely, yeah.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "By whom?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No, I think that the people we were smuggling-- the Frenchmen were fun.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they-- they didn't take their own fate seriously.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They were prisoners of war.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "So that if they were caught, there were thrown back into camp.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That's it, you know.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
